<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-lva-fixed-assets-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Select the period status (<strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-lva-fixed-assets-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Open</strong> or <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-lva-fixed-assets-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Closed</strong>). If the status is <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-lva-fixed-assets-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Closed</strong>, <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-lva-fixed-assets-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Categories</strong> on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-lva-fixed-assets-accounting.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Category details</strong> FastTab cannot be added or deleted.</td>
